<section class="about-content">
    <h3>About Me</h3>
    <p>Guan is an artist and designer deeply passionate about exploring the connections between space, emotion, philosophy, and the interaction between humans and nature. Through various forms of media, I poetically express observations and reflections on the connections and resistance between individuals and their environments. Currently holding an MFA in Media Art &amp; Installation from the Graduate School of Kyoto Saga University of Art, I am currently based in Tokyo.</p>
	<p>contact me:　<a href="mailto:Noahkan@outlook.jp">Noahkan@outlook.jp</a> </p>
</section>
	
